{
  "texts": [
    "After long and intensive discussions, a political agreement was reached on 8 December 2023.",
    "Therefore, it can be expected that the EU AI Act will soon be officially adopted by the EU Parliament and the EU Council followed by the publication in the EU's Official Journal to enter into force.",
    "It should be noted that the majority of the Act's provisions will apply after a two-year grace period with some exceptions particularly with regard to prohibitions and foundation models.",
    "The forthcoming AI Act will establish a European regulatory framework for providers and users of AI systems.",
    "The obligations will depend on the level of risk associated with the respective systems."
  ]
}